<%- include("partials/header", { pageTitle: "About" }) %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
    <body class="about-body">
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
        <main class="about-page">
            <section class="about-hero">
                 <div class="about-hero-bg">
                    <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Luxury retreat cabin">
                </div>
                <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
                <div class="about-hero-content">
                    <h1>We didn't set out<br>to build a company.</h1>
                    <p>
                        We set out to find
                        a place to breathe.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="story-section">
                <div class="story-grid">
                <div class="story-copy">
                    <span class="section-label">
                    OUR STORY
                    </span>
                    <h2>
                    This started
                    <br>
                    with a feeling.
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                    The morning light came in slowly
                    through the wooden windows.
                    Dust floating in the air.
                    Trees moving quietly outside.
                    For the first time in months,
                    we sat down without reaching
                    for our phones.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                    Coffee stayed warm in our hands.
                    The room smelled like cedar,
                    linen, and fresh air after rain.
                    Nothing extraordinary happened.
                    But somehow,
                    we felt lighter there.
                    </p>
                    <blockquote>
                    But it didn't feel like anything.
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="story-image">
                    <img src="/images/about-story.png">
                </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="about-philosophy">
                <span class="section-label">
                OUR PHILOSOPHY
                </span>
                <h2>
                A stay should not compete
                for your attention.
                <span>
                    It should create
                </span>
                space for your thoughts
                to return.
                </h2>
            </section>
            <section class="moments-section">
                <div class="moments-top">
                    <span class="section-label">
                        THE MOMENTS THAT MATTER
                    </span>
                    <h2>
                        The feeling
                        was always hidden
                        in the small things.
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="moments-grid">
                    <div class="moment-card large">
                        <img src="/images/moment1.jpg">
                        <p>
                        Morning coffee
                        with no notifications.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="moment-card">
                        <img src="/images/moment2.jpg">
                        <p>
                        Rain against
                        wooden windows.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="moment-card">
                        <img src="/images/moment3.png">
                        <p>
                        Cozy Cooking 
                        with people you love.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="moment-card wide">
                        <img src="/images/moment4.png">
                        <p>
                        Vintage rooms filled with
                        warm light and quiet evenings.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="about-world">
                <div class="world-dark-overlay"></div>
                <div class="world-content">
                    <span class="section-label gold">
                        THE WORLD
                    </span>
                    <h2>
                        Across forests,
                        coastlines,
                        mountains,
                        and hidden landscapes —
                        <em>
                        we kept finding
                        the same thing.
                        </em>
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        People searching
                        for stillness.
                    </p>
                    <div class="world-globe">
                        <img
                        src="/images/about-world.png"
                        alt="Luxury earth globe">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="belief-section">
                <span class="section-label">
                WHAT WE BELIEVE & OUR PROMISE
                </span>
                <div class="belief-grid">
                    <div class="belief-card">
                        <h3>We believe luxury is not excess.
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                        It is silence.
                        Space.
                        Light.
                        Time.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="belief-divider"></div>
                    <div class="belief-card">
                        <h3>
                        The best homes
                        don't try too hard.
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                        Neither do the people
                        inside them.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="promise-inner">
                    <h2>
                        Every stay comes
                        with our word.
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        If you arrive and it doesn't
                        feel the way we described —
                        the light,
                        the quiet,
                        the host,
                        the whole thing —
                        tell us.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We'll fix it or refund it.
                        No screenshots.
                        No case numbers.
                    </p>
                    <blockquote class="promise-block">
                        We'd rather lose money
                        than lose your trust.
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="about-ending">
                <div class="ending-overlay"></div>
                <div class="ending-content">
                <h2>
                    Maybe the best journeys
                    are not about escaping life.
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Maybe they are about
                    returning to it differently.
                </p>
                <a href="/homeList">
                    Explore Stays →
                </a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </body>
</html>